# PR Checklist

## Before Opening

- [ ] Branch named per convention (`feat/`, `fix/`, `docs/`, `chore/`)
- [ ] Conventional commit messages with issue reference (`#123`)
- [ ] Scope is single-purpose; shared types + consumers updated together
- [ ] `pnpm lint`, `pnpm typecheck`, `pnpm test` pass locally
- [ ] No secrets, `.env` files, or debug logging committed

## MR Description

- [ ] **Summary**: what changed and why (1–3 bullets)
- [ ] **Test plan**: concrete steps reviewer can follow
- [ ] Links to feature spec, ADR, or GitLab issue
- [ ] Screenshots/video for UI or 3D visual changes
- [ ] Breaking changes called out explicitly

## Contract Changes

- [ ] `packages/shared` updated first if types/events changed
- [ ] `api-contracts.md` updated for REST/WS changes
- [ ] Both `apps/web` and `apps/api` compile against new shared types
- [ ] Migration notes included if Prisma schema changed

## Performance & Scale

- [ ] LOD / instancing considered for new 3D geometry
- [ ] Agent/building counts respect phase limits in canonical-numbers
- [ ] No regression in WS message volume (diffs, not full state dumps)

## Final Gate

- [ ] CI green (lint, typecheck, tests)
- [ ] Self-reviewed using `review-checklist.mdc`
- [ ] Reviewer assigned; labels/milestone set
- [ ] MR description updated if review feedback changed behavior
